Let&#39;s suppose I&#39;m developing a class library using the new MSBuild 15.0 project format and my library has a dependency that should be within a certain version range. For a sake of this example, let&#39;s say it needs Newtonsoft.Json version 8 but for whatever reason versions 9 and 10 aren&#39;t good for it, something like this:

